pgmetrics is a good metrics tool give a glance of the database information
==========================================================================================

wget https://github.com/rapidloop/pgmetrics/releases/download/v1.7.0/pgmetrics_1.7.0_linux_amd64.tar.gz
tar xfz pgmetrics_1.7.0_linux_amd64.tar.gz
cd pgmetrics_1.7.0_linux_amd64
./pgmetrics --help


To generate the file
./pgmetrics -t 3 -U postgres -h /tmp -f human -o ./log_day.json testdb
